data.description: This stunning home boasts elegance, beauty, space, and amenities! Located on lake with private boat dock and gorgeous views this semi open-concept home features lovely light-stained floors running throughout, 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, half bath. Layout includes Formal Dining for elegant entertaining, spacious sunroom/ breakfast area overlooking views of lake, kitchen designed for convenience & practicality, large living room with a handsome fireplace, Master w/ an en-suite bathroom, and his and hers closets on one side of home with 2 more bedrooms, hall bath on other side. Enjoy entertaining on deck overlooking lake. Large 2 car garage with separate golf cart entrance. Conveniently located to shopping, dining, and an easy commute to Fort Bragg.
